      "creatureType": "",
      "blurb": "",
      "publicNotes": "<h3>Conversion notes (this module)</h3><p><strong>Role:</strong> the castle's living grotesques — <strong>eight</strong> four-armed gargoyles roost in pairs atop the four minarets (D8) and watch the landing ledges (D7). <strong>Air approach:</strong> non-stealthy fliers crossing high draw 4 of the 8; fliers hugging walls or water draw @UUID[Compendium.cotct-pf2e-conversion.cotct-actors.Actor.aerilayaBanshe01]{Aerilaya} instead (the gargoyles have learned to keep clear of her). They do not retreat from a fight.</p>",
